title: STOP THE EXCUSES
itunes:title: STOP THE EXCUSES
itunes:subtitle: Motiversity
description:
HOW DARE YOU! How dare you complain. How dare you give up. How dare you fall back. How dare you say you're done. How dare you say it's over. Your struggles are valid but there is someone out there who is dying for what you have. The life you are living, the air you can breathe. Embrace the struggles you are going through, they will make you stronger. This is a powerful new motivational speech and our latest release with Coach Pain (https://bit.ly/CoachPainMotiversity). Music by Audiomachine (https://www.youtube.com/audiomachine) and Whitesand (https://www.youtube.com/c/WhitesandComposer).

Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
